@startuml
!theme plain
title Prediction Cards - Control Flow Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "Frontend\n(React)" as Frontend
participant "WalletClient" as Wallet
participant "PredictionCards\nAPI" as API
participant "PredictionCards\nSmart Contract" as Contract
participant "Aeternity\nBlockchain" as Blockchain
participant "Process Prediction\nService" as ProcessService
participant "Oracle\nService" as OracleService

== Prediction Creation ==
User -> Frontend: Create new prediction
Frontend -> Wallet: Check wallet connection
Wallet --> Frontend: Account info
Frontend -> API: create_prediction(asset, price, times, NFT images)
API -> Contract: create_prediction()
Contract -> Blockchain: Store prediction data
Blockchain --> Contract: Confirmation
Contract --> API: Prediction created
API --> Frontend: Prediction ID
Frontend --> User: Display prediction

== NFT Renting ==
User -> Frontend: Rent NFT (outcome)
Frontend -> Wallet: Check balance
Wallet --> Frontend: Balance confirmed
Frontend -> API: rent_nft(prediction_id, option, deposit, price_per_ms)
API -> Contract: rent_nft()
Contract -> Contract: Validate rental
Contract -> Blockchain: Update NFT state
Blockchain --> Contract: Confirmation
Contract --> API: NFT rented
API --> Frontend: Rental confirmed
Frontend --> User: Display rental status

== Additional Deposit ==
User -> Frontend: Deposit more to NFT
Frontend -> API: deposit_to_nft(prediction_id, option, amount)
API -> Contract: deposit_to_nft()
Contract -> Blockchain: Update deposit
Blockchain --> Contract: Confirmation
Contract --> API: Deposit added
API --> Frontend: Success
Frontend --> User: Updated balance

== Prediction End & Processing ==
ProcessService -> ProcessService: Scheduled task triggers
ProcessService -> Blockchain: Query predictions in CLOSED state
Blockchain --> ProcessService: List of closed predictions
ProcessService -> Contract: ask_for_winning_option(prediction_id)
Contract -> Blockchain: Create oracle query
Blockchain --> Contract: Query created
Contract --> ProcessService: Oracle query initiated

== Oracle Response ==
OracleService -> OracleService: Scheduled task triggers
OracleService -> Blockchain: Check for pending queries
Blockchain --> OracleService: Oracle queries
OracleService -> OracleService: Fetch asset price
OracleService -> Blockchain: Respond to oracle query
Blockchain --> OracleService: Response recorded

ProcessService -> ProcessService: Monitor oracle response
ProcessService -> Contract: process_oracle_response(prediction_id)
Contract -> Blockchain: Get oracle response
Blockchain --> Contract: Price data
Contract -> Contract: Determine winning option
Contract -> Contract: Calculate winner (longest renter)
Contract -> Blockchain: Update prediction state to ORACLE_RESOLVED
Blockchain --> Contract: State updated
Contract --> ProcessService: Processing complete

== Reward Claiming ==
User -> Frontend: View holdings
Frontend -> API: get_prediction_state(prediction_id)
API -> Contract: Query state
Contract --> API: Prediction resolved
API --> Frontend: Winning option & rewards
Frontend --> User: Display claimable rewards

User -> Frontend: Claim rewards
Frontend -> API: claim(prediction_id, option)
API -> Contract: claim()
Contract -> Contract: Calculate reward share
Contract -> Contract: Verify renting duration
Contract -> Blockchain: Transfer rewards
Blockchain --> Contract: Transfer confirmed
Contract -> Contract: Update NFT owner (longest renter)
Contract -> Blockchain: Update ownership
Blockchain --> Contract: Ownership updated
Contract --> API: Rewards claimed
API --> Frontend: Success
Frontend --> User: Rewards received

== Oracle Extension ==
OracleService -> OracleService: Periodic extension task
OracleService -> Blockchain: Extend oracle TTL
Blockchain --> OracleService: Oracle extended

@enduml
